text: Lana Osiņina (born 5 October 2002) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a forward for Sieviešu Futbola Līga club Rīgas FS and the Latvia women's national team. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers Category:Rīgas FS players
